description: [FIVEHANDS](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0618) has the ability to enumerate files on a compromised host in order to encrypt files with specific extensions.(Citation: CISA AR21-126A FIVEHANDS May 2021)(Citation: NCC Group Fivehands June 2021)
